  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND CHAPTER 922, LOCAL AND PRIVATE LAWS OF 2013, AS LAST AMENDED BY CHAPTER 938, LOCAL AND PRIVATE LAWS OF 2022, TO EXTEND THE REPEAL DATE ON THE LAW THAT AUTHORIZES THE GOVERNING AUTHORITIES OF THE CITY OF HORN LAKE, MISSISSIPPI, TO LEVY A TAX UPON HOTEL AND MOTEL ROOM RENTALS, WHICH SHALL BE USED TO PROMOTE THE CITY'S TOURISM AND ECONOMIC DEVELOPMENT; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
